thread.title_full: Thunder sign former OSU Cowboy Cobbins, Farrakhan to deals

author: Associated Press
title: Thunder sign former OSU Cowboy Cobbins, Farrakhan to deals
text:
OKLAHOMA CITY -- The Oklahoma City Thunder have signed former Oklahoma State forward Michael Cobbins and guard Mustapha Farrakhan.
General manager Sam Presti announced the signings. Terms of the deals were not disclosed.
Cobbins is a 6-foot-8-inch forward who was twice voted to the Big 12 All-Defense team.
Farrakhan is a 6-foot-4-inch guard who played for four teams in the NBA D-League in 2011-2012 and 2012-2013. He played professionally in Australia in 2013-2014 and played collegiately at Virginia.
 NBA Basketball Pro Men Associated Press
